The paper deals with computational problems in homotopy theory, which is a branch of algebraic topology. The paper also involves the computation of homology groups, which is a topic in discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The paper deals with the computation of homotopy groups, which is a topic in geometric topology (cs.GT). The paper also involves the computation of mappings between topological spaces, which is a topic in computational topology (cs.SD). Finally, the paper deals with the computation of algorithms for simplicial sets, which is a topic in systems and control (cs.SY).
